{"version": "https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1", "title": "\u57fa\u5ca9\u6587\u6863", "home_page_url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/", "feed_url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_json_updated.json", "description": "Minecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u5f00\u53d1\u6587\u6863", "icon": null, "authors": [], "language": "zh", "items": [{"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/category/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/category/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/", "title": "\u6280\u672f", "content_html": "<h1>\u6280\u672f</h1>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/blog/category/\u6280\u672f.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T06:00:26.635016+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T06:00:26.635010+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/archive/2024/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/archive/2024/", "title": "2024", "content_html": "<h1>2024</h1>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/blog/archive/2024.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T06:00:26.602059+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T06:00:26.602053+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/general/json-ui/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/general/json-ui/", "title": "JSON UI", "content_html": "<h1>JSON UI</h1>\n<p><strong>JSON UI</strong>\u662fMinecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u4e2d\u7528\u4e8e\u5b9a\u4e49\u6e38\u620f\u7528\u6237\u754c\u9762\u7684\u7cfb\u7edf\u3002\u8be5\u7cfb\u7edf\u4f7f\u7528JSON\u683c\u5f0f\u7684\u6570\u636e\u6587\u4ef6\u58f0\u660e\u754c\u9762\u7684\u5e03\u5c40\u3001\u63a7\u4ef6\u548c\u4ea4\u4e92\u903b\u8f91\uff0c\u5141\u8bb8\u8d44\u6e90\u5305\u8986\u76d6\u6216\u6269\u5c55\u6e38\u620f\u5185\u754c\u9762\u3002</p>\n<p>JSON UI\u6ca1\u6709\u72ec\u7acb\u7684\u683c\u5f0f\u7248\u672c\u63a7\u5236\uff0c\u66f4\u6